---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Canton Fair Guide"
  description="A practical Canton Fair hub for overseas buyers covering phases, registration, hotels, booth planning, supplier questions, and follow-up."
  canonical="/canton-fair/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <div class="hub-hero">
      <div class="page-header">
        <span class="eyebrow">Canton Fair Guide</span>
        <h1>Prepare for the Canton Fair like a serious buyer.</h1>
        <p>
          The fair is easier to use when you know which phase to attend, where to stay, how to organize booth visits, and
          what information to collect from suppliers.
        </p>
        <div class="inline-actions">
          <a class="button" href="/tools/canton-fair-buyer-checklist/">Open buyer checklist</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/blog/best-area-to-stay-guangzhou-canton-fair/">Choose hotel area</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hub-visual" aria-label="Canton Fair preparation summary">
        <div class="hub-stat"><span class="icon-badge">P1</span><div><strong>Phase</strong><p>Match fair dates to your product category.</p></div></div>
        <div class="hub-stat"><span class="icon-badge">ID</span><div><strong>Badge</strong><p>Prepare registration details and business cards.</p></div></div>
        <div class="hub-stat"><span class="icon-badge">Q</span><div><strong>Questions</strong><p>Ask suppliers the same comparison questions.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Who this guide is for</h2>
        <p>
          This guide is for overseas buyers attending the Canton Fair for the first time or returning with a more
          focused product list. It is especially useful for small importers, Amazon and Shopify sellers, wholesalers,
          and business owners comparing Chinese suppliers in person.
        </p>

        <h2>Common problems buyers run into</h2>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Booking flights before confirming the correct fair phase</li>
          <li>Choosing a hotel that adds too much daily transport time</li>
          <li>Collecting brochures without clear supplier notes</li>
          <li>Asking different questions at each booth, making comparison difficult</li>
          <li>Waiting too long after the fair to request quotes, samples, and follow-up details</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What to prepare</h2>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Confirm whether your products fit Phase 1, Phase 2, or Phase 3</li>
          <li>Prepare buyer badge registration details and business cards</li>
          <li>Book a hotel with practical access to the Pazhou exhibition area</li>
          <li>Create a booth note template before entering the halls</li>
          <li>Prepare supplier questions about MOQ, samples, certificates, lead time, and payment terms</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Helpful resources for buyers</h2>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <a class="resource-card" href="/blog/canton-fair-first-time-buyer-guide/">
            <span class="card-kicker">Guide</span>
            <h3>First-Time Buyer Guide</h3>
            <p>Phases, badge basics, booth planning, supplier questions, and follow-up.</p>
            <strong>Read guide</strong>
          </a>
          <a class="resource-card" href="/tools/canton-fair-buyer-checklist/">
            <span class="card-kicker">Tool</span>
            <h3>Buyer Checklist</h3>
            <p>Confirm phase, badge, hotel area, questions, and follow-up process.</p>
            <strong>Open checklist</strong>
          </a>
          <a class="resource-card" href="/tools/supplier-comparison-sheet/">
            <span class="card-kicker">Template</span>
            <h3>Supplier Sheet</h3>
            <p>Track MOQ, samples, trade terms, and communication quality.</p>
            <strong>Open template</strong>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="notice-box">
          <h2>First visit tip</h2>
          <p>Confirm your phase and hotel area before booking flights so your fair days stay focused and efficient.</p>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/blog/canton-fair-first-time-buyer-guide/">Read buyer guide</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
